    <item>
      <title>Re: Quest History?</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Quests&amp;message.id=665#M665</link>
      <description>Currently we have three different types of "Quests".  Tasks are usually short tasks that you complete which was introduced with Omens of War.  Shared Tasks are the missions that we introduced in Dragons of Norrath where your group gets the missions together to complete.  &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We also have the ability to use the task window with quests.  You can have multiple quests going at the same time in the task window.  On completion of a quest it will save the 50 more recent quests that you have completed in the quest history tab.  &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Currently there are only a few quests in the game that use the task window like the cultural tradeskill quests and the Dragons of Norrath progression quests.  We plan on using it a lot more in the future.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hopefully that explanation wasn't to confusing with the entire task/quest talk!</description>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Mar 2005 19:53:11 GMT</pubDate>
