      <title>Re: Quest History?</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Quests&amp;message.id=671#M671</link>
      <description>The shared tasks are just another form of tasks that you and your group do.  They are a little different than quests.  Most shared tasks will be done more than once.  Quests that take more time to complete and usually are more involved which is why we display them compared to a task that is meant to only take a minimal amount of time.</description>
